  "title": "The Direx Board Faces a Demand",
  "summary": "The Direx Board of the Corporate Sector Authority convenes at CSA Headquarters to address a crisis sparked when Security Division's Colonel Gren Delede led Authority warships into battle near Nar Shaddaa, alongside extra-territorial allies, bringing the CSA to the brink of war with the Galactic Empire. Merr-Sonn CEO Gimel Daleth opens by charging Delede with a Class A infraction and even accusing ExO McKnight, while corporate representatives Roland Sienar of KDY, Milo Sienar of SFS, and the newcomer Krysten Rheas of FLS weigh the Empire's escalating demands, including the dismantling of Authority fleets. Prex Rinn Vakil, a friend of the ExO, struggles to contain the momentum toward a no-confidence vote as CEC's Shannon argues for trying Delede themselves rather than capitulating to the Sith advisor Darth Malign. Legal Viceprex Xerxes Kherzen's testimony, revealing that Delede ignored his counsel to withdraw, tips the board, which votes to strip Delede of rank and extradite him to the Empire while releasing the prisoner Antoine Dareus.",
